parameters: Sylvia: No way... Lord Zena... Impossible...

Luuna: It seems he was a mistaken prince who should not have come
here.
Zena: Didn't I say I'm tough? Ufufufufu...
Lucia: It seems your sister didn't know.
Sylvia: The forbidden book of immortality...

Zena: That's right. I am a prince of the great magical nation of
Valentia. I have mastered all kinds of forbidden magic.
Zena: Immortality is one of those magics.

Lucia: Luuna, you've lost. Beg for your life and I might spare you.
Fufufu...

Sylvia: Lord Zena, Luuna's existence is too dangerous. Quickly, use
the Threads of Death.

Zena: Indeed. I didn't expect to encounter a sorceress of this
caliber.
Luuna: (I'm prepared for death. But before the end...)
Luuna: Lucia, this is as far as I go.
Luuna: Lucia, there's something I want you to hear before the end.
Luuna: I want you to wake up. To return to how you were before...
Lucia: Fufufu... What a laughable thing to say.

Lucia: Unfortunately, tears won't work on me. I am a woman after all.
Kukuku...
Luuna: Do you remember? You used to cry like this... all the time.

Lucia: Tears? I've long forgotten about such things. Fufu... Hahaha...
Ahahahaha!
Luuna: Lucia, do you think I haven't noticed?
Luuna: When you lie, you have a habit of your pinky trembling.
Luuna: What are you hiding? Even at a time like this...
Luuna: It's alright. There must be some serious reason.
Lucia: Fufu... What nonsensical things are you saying, I wonder.
Luuna: Lucia, your pinky is still trembling, isn't it?

Luuna: But... seeing your pinky tremble like that puts me at ease.
Even if you don't say it in words.
Luuna: That trembling pinky tells me everything.

Lucia: Fufu... How foolish. Luuna, it would be better if you just died
quickly and faded from my memory.

Luuna: Before I die, I want to remember... the memories with you...
the good times...

Luuna: At the end... I want to recall the memories with you... I want
to remember...
Luuna: Big sister Lucia~! This flower is so beautiful, isn't it~...!
Lucia: The flowers over here are beautiful too~...!
Luuna: Lady Lucia, when are you going to confess to him~?
Lucia: Silly~ Luuna, don't say embarrassing things~.
Luuna: Oh come on~ I hate you, Lady Lucia~!
Lucia: Sorry... Luuna, don't be mad.
Luuna: No way~ I'll never forgive you~.
Lucia: Luuna~ What is it~? You were just angry a moment ago~.
Luuna: Just pretending to be angry~. Lady Lucia~ I love you~!
Luuna: Big sister Lucia, I love you~!
Luuna: Lady Lucia~...! Big sister Lucia~...!
Luuna: Lucia... thank you for the beautiful memories.

Luuna: (Goodbye... Noah... Regnus Grahardt... Mr. Luca... Lady
Ceres... Rinny... Becky... everyone...)
[Vice Captain] Lady Ceres, what's the matter?
The news of Luuna's death spread among the resistance.
Luuna and her companions were defeated.
Now, everything has come to an end.
